methods.name: initialize

args.name: settlementAssetId
args.desc: - 0 for ALGO, ASA ID for USDCA

methods.desc: Initialize marketplace escrow

methods.name: setSettlementCurrency
methods.desc: Update settlement currency (admin only)

methods.name: setRates
methods.desc: Update configurable rates (only creator)

methods.name: createTrade

args.name: amount
args.desc: - Already divided amount (in microAlgos or microASA)

methods.desc:
Create trade (buyer initiates)

UI MUST divide instrument price by 100,000 before calling this

methods.name: escrowTrade
methods.desc:
Escrow trade - buyer locks funds (ALGO)

Group transaction structure:
[0] Payment (buyer to contract)
[1] Application call (this method)

methods.name: escrowTradeWithAsset
methods.desc:
Escrow trade - buyer locks funds (ASA)

Group transaction structure:
[0] AssetTransfer (buyer to contract)
[1] Application call (this method)

methods.name: escrowTradeAsFinancier
methods.desc:
Escrow trade as financier - third party locks funds (ALGO)

Group transaction structure:
[0] Payment (financier to contract)
[1] Application call (this method)

methods.name: escrowTradeAsFinancierWithAsset
methods.desc:
Escrow trade as financier - third party locks funds (ASA)

Group transaction structure:
[0] AssetTransfer (financier to contract)
[1] Application call (this method)

methods.name: executeTrade
methods.desc:
Execute trade - seller transfers RWA instrument and receives payment (ALGO)

Group transaction structure:
[0] Asset transfer (seller sends instrument NFT to buyer/marketplace)
[1] Payment (regulator tax payment from seller)
[2] Application call (this method - triggers internal payments)

methods.name: executeTradeWithAsset
methods.desc:
Execute trade - seller transfers RWA instrument and receives payment (ASA)

Group transaction structure:
[0] Asset transfer (seller sends instrument NFT to buyer/marketplace)
[1] AssetTransfer (regulator tax payment from seller)
[2] Application call (this method - triggers internal payments)

methods.name: acknowledgePayment
methods.desc:
Acknowledge payment - seller confirms receipt and triggers regulator refund (ALGO)

Group transaction structure:
[0] Payment (regulator sends refund to seller)
[1] Application call (this method)

methods.name: acknowledgePaymentWithAsset
methods.desc:
Acknowledge payment - seller confirms receipt and triggers regulator refund (ASA)

Group transaction structure:
[0] AssetTransfer (regulator sends refund to seller)
[1] Application call (this method)

methods.name: expireTrade
methods.desc: Expire trade - admin function to cancel and refund

methods.name: getTrade
methods.desc: Get trade details

methods.name: getTradeMetadata
methods.desc: Get trade metadata

methods.name: getTradesByBuyer
methods.desc: Get trades by buyer

methods.name: getTradesBySeller
methods.desc: Get trades by seller

methods.name: calculateEscrowCost
methods.desc: Calculate escrow cost (amount + fee)

methods.name: calculateRegulatorCosts
methods.desc: Calculate regulator costs

methods.name: getPaymentConfig
methods.desc: Get payment configuration for UI
